THE RIFLEMAN -1x02- Home Ranch    (10/7/1958)

Two hired hands of a wealthy cattleman, who has been using the ranch for grazing his cattle, demand that Lucas move out. When Lucas refuses, he is beaten and dragged and then the ranch house is burned down.

Starring: Chuck Connors as Lucas McCain and  Johnny Crawford as Mark McCain
Guest stars: Don Kennedy (Clyde), Lee Farr (Sam Montgomery), Steve Rowland (Billy Lehigh), Harold J. Stone (Oat Jackford), Rodolfo Hoyos Jr. (Pablo) 
First aired: 7 October 1958
